<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Nasrallah Pledges Continued Resistance </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1306072994 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0430 GMT 13 Jun 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1306072994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hizballah Secretary General Hasan Nasrallah has 
pledged to continue the jihad and resistance and not to 
capitulate regardless of Israeli reactions. 
  He called for putting internal differences aside at this 
