statements and allusions several times in the past weeks. 
  The source concluded his statement by saying: It is 
noteworthy that the picture conveyed to the custodian of the two 
holy mosques by Mr. Lakhdar Ibrahimi, the current mediator, from 
President 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih is completely different in spirit 
and substance from the statements of al-Iryani to whom, were it 
not for our eagerness to clarify facts about him for public 
