is arrogant and blood-thirsty. This objective is impossible to 
achieve. The Armed Forces of the DRY supported by thousands of 
our people who have enlisted in their ranks have taken the 
responsibility of defending the DRY and its sovereignty, and 
will never allow the new invading aggressors to continue 
inflicting their folly and recklessness against the lives and 
possessions of our people. Defeat is awaiting the aggressors 
and victory is near, God willing. 

