BFN 

  [Excerpt] A responsible source at the Defense Ministry of 
the Democratic Republic of Yemen has categorically denied that 
Rayyan Airport [serving al-Mukalla] had been rendered inoperable 
or had suffered any kind of damage. The source said all 
democratic Yemen's airports with the exception of that at Ataq 
were operational. The source expressed amazement that it was 
Israel radio which had carried the report by the military 
spokesman in Sanaa that northern forces yesterday evening 
allegedly shelled al-Mukalla's airport. [passage omitted] 

