<F P=105>  Urdu </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In Afghanistan, President Borhanoddin Rabbani's 
government has submitted a two-point peace formula for the 
restoration of durable peace in the country. The formula 
provides for the ceasing forthwith of rocket attacks on Kabul, 
honoring the cease-fire, and opening up all highways leading to 
Kabul. It also proposes the setting up of an authoritative 
nongovernmental commission to initiate work on the 
Representative Council and Grand Assembly. 

