  [Text] President 'Ali Akbar Hashemi-Rafsanjani received 
Bosnian Foreign Minister Irfan Ljubljankic today. The president 
praised the brave holy war of the Muslims of Bosnia-Herzegovina 
against the Serb aggressors, and said that the Islamic Republic 
of Iran will continue to stand alongside the Muslim people of 
Bosnia. The president also stressed the need for comprehensive 
international support in realizing the rights of the Bosnian 
Muslims. 
  Emphasizing the determination of the Muslims of 
Bosnia-Herzegovina in defending their beliefs and existence, and 
speaking on behalf of the president, the government and the 
people of his country, the Bosnian foreign minister thanked the 
revolutionary people and government of Iran for their 
humanitarian aid. 

