BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 12 Jun (MENA)--Tahir al-Masri, speaker of the 
Jordanian House of Representatives, left Cairo today after a 
two-day visit during which he held talks with Egyptian officials 
on bilateral ties and Arab and regional issues of mutual 
interest. 

