  [Text] Israel has decided to boycott the neofascist 
ministers in Italy, but will not announce this decision 
publicly. Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres told his Italian 
counterpart Antonio Martino in Luxembourg this evening that 
Israel will not take any steps against the Italian Government in 
the wake of the neofascist ministers' appointment. 

