<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] A responsible source at the Ministry of Defense 
of the Democratic Republic of Yemen has said that the forces of 
the ruling military regime in Sanaa continued today their 
desperate attacking attempts on all the battlefronts. They 
launched random rocket and artillery attacks on residential 
quarters and peaceful villages in expression of the regime's 
hysterical state and inability to achieve any progress on all 
the battlefronts. 
  In a statement to the ADEN NEWS AGENCY, the source pointed 
out that the Armed Forces of the Democratic Republic of Yemen 
faced with legendary courage these desperate attempted 
offensives. They inflicted crushing blows on the invading 
forces resulting in heavy losses. The source pointed out that 
eight hostile tanks, three armored cars and two Katyusha rocket 
vehicles were destroyed. The northern troops also suffered 
hundreds of dead and wounded. [passage omitted] 

