<H3> <TI>   Saudis Said To Deploy Forces Near Border </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Saudis Said To Deploy Forces Near Border </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1306174894 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1727 GMT 13 
