<H3> <TI>   Security Forces Kill `Terrorists,' Seize Arms </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Security Forces Kill `Terrorists,' Seize Arms </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1306195694 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 13 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1306195694 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] According to a statement released today, the 
security forces, in operations lasting a week and ending today, 
eliminated 11 terrorists and recovered an important quantity of 
weapons, including submachine guns, shotguns and automatic 
pistols. The operations were carried out in the provinces of 
Algiers, Chlef and Blida. 

</TEXT>

