<F P=104>  Paris Radio France International </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Concerning Western Sahara, we note this statement by 
the Algerian foreign minister, as reported by the Moroccan daily 
L'OPINION. According to L'OPINION, Mr. Mohammed Salah Dembri 
said that a political solution that could bypass a referendum in 
