<F P=100> IRAQ </F>
<H3> <TI>   Talabani, Barzani Discuss Kurdistan Situation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Talabani, Barzani Discuss Kurdistan Situation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1406172694 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan 
in Arabic 1608 GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1406172694 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan 
in Arabic 1608 GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=105> Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A delegation from the Patriotic Union of Kurdistan 
[PUK], led by PUK Secretary General brother Jalal Talabani, met 
with a delegation from the Kurdistan Democratic Party [KDP], led 
by KDP Leader Mas'ud Barzani, in the city of Silopi in Turkey at 
1030 yesterday. A Turkish Government delegation attended the 
meeting, which was held to discuss the means and possibilities 
of normalizing the situation in Kurdistan, speeding up the 
agreements already approved by the two parties, and 
consolidating security and stability in the Kurdistan region. 

</TEXT>

